About Rocco's Tacos
Slide 1 of 4
Slide 2 of 4
Slide 3 of 4
Slide 4 of 4
hero gallery paused, press to play images slides
Playing hero gallery, press to pause images slides
Rocco’s Tacos offers a true taste of Mexico within a fun casual environment. When you first step through the door you become part of the atmosphere, joining a diverse crowd enjoying flavors picked directly from Mexico.
Enjoy guacamole prepared table-side, choose from more than 200 tequilas, and sip a margarita made with our signature house-crafted sour mix — made right on the premises. Rocco’s offers a diverse menu with distinct attention to detail, including hand-pressed corn tortillas cooked fresh on the comal in our kitchen, just as they are made in kitchens throughout our neighbors to the south.
Experience bold, authentic Mexican flavors and handcrafted cocktails at Rocco’s Tacos. From our Signature Guacamole made fresh table-side to house-made tortillas, flavorful tacos, and crispy churros, every dish is crafted to deliver unforgettable flavor — whether you're here for lunch, dinner, weekend brunch, or late-night bites, we’ve got you covered.
